Boudin is a ubiquitous
sausage of Cajun Country,

58
00:03:30,417 --> 00:03:32,867
and judging by the line
up at the drive through,

59
00:03:32,902 --> 00:03:35,974
Billy's Boudin is
pretty damn popular.

60
