wouldn't be complete

68
00:03:59,308 --> 00:04:03,967
without some cracklins,
and of course, a cold beer.

69
00:04:04,002 --> 00:04:06,004
My father's
first language is French.

70
00:04:06,038 --> 00:04:08,317
